5:30pm - 7:00pm<div style="">
<em>Second annual bike celebration of cooperatives here in Portland, Oregon! This year we are planning a great Co-cycle fundraising event; a Co-op Scavenger Hunt ending with competitive Co-op Trivia and party! Originally inspired by Co-cycle and building off the great energy of Pedalpalooza we are excited to create greater awareness of co-ops in a festive atmosphere! Please bring money to help fundraise for Co-cycle! #coopalooza2013</em>
