<dl>
<dt style=""><a name="11-3740" style="">BIKE SHOP LOVE DAY</a>
<a href="http://shift2bikes.org/cal/viewpp2013.php#11-3740"><img border="0" src="viewpp2013_files/chain.gif" alt="Link" title="Link to this event"></a>
<img align="left" src="viewpp2013_files/ff.gif" alt="FF" title="Family Friendly">
</dt><dd><div style=""><a href="http://maps.google.com/?bounds=45.389771,-122.829208|45.659647,-122.404175&q=SW+4th+and+Jefferson" target="_BLANK">SW 4th and Jefferson</a> <a href="http://trimet.org/go/cgi-bin/plantrip.cgi?to=SW+4th+and+Jefferson&by=7:30+a.m.&on=06/11/13" target="_BLANK" title="TriMet trip planner"><img alt="Take Trimet" src="viewpp2013_files/trimetrose.gif" border="0"></a></div>
7:30am, All Day Long!<div style="">
<em>Portland is home to dozens of bike shops, each one staffed by hardworking mechanics and salespeople doing their best to make your ride awesome.
