10:00am - 1:00pm<div style="">
<em>A pedal tour of Works Progress Administration (WPA) sponsored projects in Portland. Visit and learn about the extensive WPA art collection at the Portland Art Museum and public works such as Paul Grellerts mural at the Morrison Street post office, Skidmore Fountain, and Woody Guthrie Circle. Tour departs from the Portland Art Museum courtyard. 
