<br>We'll supply a smattering of unicycles and patient support for anyone, young or old who wants to learn to ride one. &nbsp;You'll need to bring your own gloves, pads and a helmet if you care to protect any of the body parts those items traditionally cover.
<br>This is a family friendly event sponsored by Portland's own Unicycle Bastards. If you don't like us, don't come</em>
