6:00pm - 6:00am, Depart MAX at 6:30pm, return to PDX late morning<div style="">
<em>Whether you're "funemployed" or can get off work a little early, a quick little weekday camping excursion is a lot of fun. A 10 mile ride (approx.) from the MAX in Gresham to Oxbow on the Sandy. Moderate traffic/terrain. We should get there before dark, but remember bike lights. You can probably make it to work on time Tuesday! Campsites $22/night, divvied up appropriately. Bring all the things you would need for an overnight camping trip. Previous bike camping experience recommended. Grocery stop in Gresham. &nbsp;Limited to 12 people, register here: <a href="http://oxbowjune2013s24o.eventbrite.com/" class="smallhref">http://oxbowjune2013s24o.eventbrite.com/</a></em>
